Title: Healthbuddy HBBPM02 Bp Monitor
Description: Featured InstrumentWith a philanthropic objective of reaching out to the masses, Healthbuddy uncovers an ally you’d prefer all your life, the ‘Digital Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor’. It is designed keeping convenience, satisfaction and precision in mind.DescriptionThe term Blood Pressure refers to the pressure exerted by the circulating blood on the arteries. The blood pressure in the circulation is principally due to the pumping action of the heart. During each heartbeat, blood pressure varies between a maximum (systolic) and a minimum (diastolic) pressure. During the contraction of the heart it sends out blood into the body. This is referred to as Systolic. The pressure that is created as the heart pulls blood back through is Diastolic.Our device is proposed for the measurement of this Systolic and Diastolic arterial blood pressure and pulse pressure. Healthbuddy B.P. Check Digital Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor comes with a wide LCD screen giving you an easier reading experience along with accuracy at its best.FunctioningThis kind of digital upper-arm sphygmomanometer uses the oscillometric method to measure the blood pressure and pulse. Oscillometric method is the measuring of the fluctuations in pressure. To do the same, wrap the fitted cuff around the upper-arms. Once that is done, the monitor fills up the cuff with air.Features and BenefitsThree-fold displays (Systolic, diastolic and pulse rate)Convenient operationAccuracy in measurementEasier reading with liquid crystal digital displayNoise cancellation air pumpAccessibility up to 60 memoriesBattery Type: 4x AA batteries(not included in the pack)Battery Life: Approximately 2 months with 3 minutes usage per dayAutomatic shut down after 30seconds of inactivityOne year product warrantyOptional AC adapter (sold separately)Consists ofHealthbuddy B.P. Check Digital Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor includes the following:1x Cuff1x LCD Screen. Checking your blood pressure at home is an important part to keep a check and manage high blood pressure.For over a decade now, upper arm blood pressure measurement has been the gold standard method to guide treatment decisions. And today in this golden era of constantly improving technology, Digital blood pressure monitors are definitely a boon!Healthbuddy now makes measuring blood pressure at home easier and more accurate than ever. Home monitoring can help you keep a tab on your blood pressure in a familiar setting, make certain your medication is working, and alert you and your doctors to potential health complications.Healthbuddy B.P. Check Digital Upper Arm B. P. Monitor features:Measures systolic pressure, diastolic pressure and pulseAutomatic inflation and deflation controlRecalls last 60 readingsDate and time display for user’s convenienceLarge, easy to read digital display screenAuto-off after 30 seconds of inactivityOptional AC adapter (sold separately). Batteries exhausted?Now functioning made convenient & economical with Healthbuddy BP Check Digital Upper Arm Blood Pressure Monitor Power Adapter!!The Healthbuddy BP Check Power Adapter for Healthbuddy BP Check Blood Pressure Monitor is a need-to-have, if you own a blood pressure monitor. This serves as the positive main adapter for Healthbuddy BP Check blood pressure monitors. It has a capacity of 6 volts. It can take in anywhere from 100 – 240 volts of alternating current (AC). The cord is of a favourable length of 148cm.You can be sure you will be able to use it in the power sockets of your home.Please do note that this adaptor is not compatible with each and every Digital Blood Pressure Monitors.CAUTION: Keep the product away from water.Buy the Healthbuddy BP Check Power Adapter today and use your Healthbuddy BP Check Blood Pressure Monitor efficiently! Makes functioning convenient even when you are out of batteries!Portable sizeEasy to useConvenient cord length of 148cmInput: 100-240V AC 50/60Hz 0.5A MaxOutput: 6V DC 1.0A

Title: Infi INF1112A MDI Technology Bp Monitor(White)
Description: Infi MDI is a 3rd Generation BP Monitor with Measurement During Inflation Technology (MDIT). With MDI Technology BP Monitor checks the Blood Pressure during inflation and does not need to wait for deflation resulting in a more accurate blood pressure measurement. As blood pressure is measured during inflation it hardly creates any pressure on the arm thus allowing for consecutive blood pressure measurements with minimal deviation. Diastolic, which is more sensitive, is measured first and Systolic is measured later resulting in more accurate Diastolic readings. In short, Benifits of this New MDI Technology are more accurate results, more comfort due to less pressure on patient's arm and quicker results.

Title: Dalan Castile Beauty Soap - Cocoa Butter (Pack Of 6)
Description: Cream based beauty soap with cocoa butter base and rich cocoa fragrance. Cocoa Butter, also called Cacao Butter, is the cream-colored fat extracted from cacao seeds (cocoa beans) and used to add flavor, scent, and smoothness to chocolate, cosmetics, tanning oil, soap, and a multitude of topical lotions and creams. Cocoa Butter has been called the ultimate moisturizer, and has been used to keep skin soft and supple for centuries. It is one of the most stable, highly concentrated natural fats known, and melts at body temperature so that it is readily absorbed into the skin. Cocoa Butter is often recommended for treatment of skin conditions such as eczema and dermatitis. When applied topically, it creates a barrier between sensitive skin and the environment and also helps retain moisture. Cocoa Butter contains a number of different antioxidants that can kill off a wide range of different free radicals that destroy your skin cells and lead to premature aging. This makes it an ideal skin care product.
